<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَيُقَالُ:</span> قَدْ شَنَّ عَلَيْهِمُ الْغَارَةَ إِذَا فَرَّقَهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">تَمَّ حَدِيثُ طَلْحَةَ بْنِ عُبَيْدٍ اللَّهِ رَحِمَهُ اللَّهُ يَتْلُوهُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>حَدِيثُ أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ سَعْدِ بْنِ أَبِي وَقَّاصٍ رَحِمَهُ اللَّهُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>